{
  "stem": "13063.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Life in ghetto was really [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] full of anguish, full of forebodings, sufferings, and deprivation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we did not feel yet that our lives, our very lives, were threatened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew that people were taken off the streets many times by German parties coming in and-- and-- and catching people in the street for work, mostly for work, and returning them later.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did see it, and I was terrified.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was running away, because everybody was running.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In any house, in any cellar, you see, to hide.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "An hour, two hours, until they left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it was during the day, mostly in the morning-- morning hours, because they needed somebody to work for them at their place, at the-- at their whatever-- wherever they were stationed.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they just came into the ghetto and grabbed people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But usually they returned them from work in the-- in the evening hours.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This I-- I don't remember really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But mostly the hiding was in order not to be taken from the street somewhere to work under terrible conditions and being beaten while working.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We had sufficient-- sufficient food, perhaps, in ghetto-- sufficient bread, I would say.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not always.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sometimes, as I said, I would-- I was hungry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sometimes I was hungry because it was not a regular food supply.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sometimes there was-- there was-- there were days that food did not reach the-- the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The usual sources of food were not there, perhaps, so people were suffering hunger.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But this was, I would say, an exception to the rule.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The rule was there was enough-- enough bread, enough potatoes, and some vegetables, I would say.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was not-- no variety in food.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
